{"tid":1537692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打撚夠飛機未？？？","createTime":"2019-09-04T04:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:03:08.000Z","uid":4396,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"355941b1f6db66c0ad94c96d4e5dee0a69dc57f7","tid":1537692,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一個行動po都上唔撚到熱門呀！點撚樣贏呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快撚啲將文宣share出去Facebook、instagram、Twitter、Reddit！<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再圍爐打飛機呀！<br />\n<br />\n我地死左10個手足啦！你地係咪放棄左啦？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲幫手宣傳、檢討一下所有戰略！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求！決一不可！！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hVoV7L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hVoV7L.jpg&h=c258a34d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a376d0fd05a93e7b9dabac8d116cd4c3d748ced3","tid":1537692,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\"